targets.rawSql:
SELECT
	COUNT(DISTINCT public.git_commits.hash) as count,
	'Total Commits' AS base_repository_name,
	$__timeGroup(public.git_commits.committer_when, '${interval}', 0) AS time
FROM public.git_commits
INNER JOIN public.github_repo_info ON public.git_commits.repo_id = public.github_repo_info.repo_id
INNER JOIN public.repos ON public.git_commits.repo_id = public.repos.id
WHERE public.git_commits.committer_when IS NOT NULL AND public.git_commits.parents < 2
AND $__timeFilter(public.git_commits.committer_when) AND '${repositories:json}'::jsonb ? (public.github_repo_info.owner || '/' || public.github_repo_info.name)
AND (CASE WHEN jsonb_array_length('${repository_tags:json}'::jsonb) <> 0 THEN (public.repos.tags @> '${repository_tags:json}'::jsonb) ELSE true END)
GROUP BY time, base_repository_name
ORDER BY time, count
